<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-primary">description</span> Biểu mẫu
        </a>
<div class="w-px h-4 bg-slate-300 shrink-0"></div>
<a class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-secondary hover:text-primary transition-colors whitespace-nowrap" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">call</span> Đường dây nóng: 1900 xxxx
        </a>
