<span class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider">Diện tích (ha)</span>
</div>
<div class="w-px bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<span class="text-2xl font-black text-[#0f7a5a]">450+</span>
<span class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider">Doanh nghiệp</span>
</div>
<div class="w-px hidden sm:block bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col hidden sm:flex">
