<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 via-black/40 to-transparent opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-500 group-hover:opacity-100"></div>
<div class="absolute inset-0 p-6 flex flex-col justify-end translate-y-8 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500 ease-out">
<span class="inline-block bg-secondary text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-3 w-max">Thiên nhiên</span>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 transform transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:-translate-y-2">Khu sinh thái</h3>
<div class="overflow-hidden">
<p class="text-white/80 text-sm line-clamp-2 mb-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 delay-100 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0">Hòa mình vào thiên nhiên miệt vườn sông nước chân chất.</p>
